## 3. GitHub Automation Layer

### Repository

`shelly-calendar-buffer`

### Workflow

`.github/workflows/calendar-buffer-sync.yml`

Runs: - Every 6 hours - Or manually via workflow_dispatch

------------------------------------------------------------------------

## 4. Sync Logic Overview

File: `sync.mjs`

Key behaviors:

-   Auth via OAuth2 refresh token
-   Reads events from main calendar (via Shelly access)
-   Only syncs future events (LOOKAHEAD_DAYS = 45)
-   Writes to TARGET_CALENDAR_ID (Shelly Buffer)
-   Upsert logic (no duplicates)
-   Private visibility
-   No description/location/attendees copied

------------------------------------------------------------------------

